#: ../../source/functions/system_control/volume_control.md:1
msgid "Volume Control"
msgstr "音量控制"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/volume_control.md:3
msgid ""
"The volume control key allows controlling system audio output volume. The"
" volume on the slider would be automatically kept in sync with the system"
" volume setting."
msgstr "音量控制按键允许控制系统音频输出音量。滑块上的音量会自动与系统音量设置保持同步。"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/volume_control.md:5
msgid ""
"This key only works when the FlexDesigner is running. If this is not "
"desired, consider using the 'Scroll Wheel' key in the 'Input' category, "
"and bind the left/ right action to volume down/ up. The catch is that the"
" scroll wheel key won't be able to display the current volume."
msgstr "此按键仅在 FlexDesigner 运行时工作。如果不需要这样，请考虑使用"输入"类别中的"滚轮"按键，并将左/右操作绑定到音量降低/提高。问题是滚轮按键无法显示当前音量。"

